Okay, you.
You need some light.

131
00:08:22,169 --> 00:08:24,271
Oh, God.

132
00:08:25,139 --> 00:08:26,741
They smell bad?

133
00:08:26,774 --> 00:08:28,442
Oh, they don't
smell good, honey.

134
00:08:28,476 --> 00:08:32,380
- You're going to be there
very soon. Believe me.

135
00:08:32,413 --> 00:08:33,748
I'll get it.

136
