a pretty big chest.

178
00:10:34,869 --> 00:10:36,170
You know,
coming from New York,

179
00:10:36,203 --> 00:10:38,405
I thought you'd be
a lot more grown up.

180
00:10:38,439 --> 00:10:39,740
