181
00:10:40,774 --> 00:10:43,545
You mean, like, really kiss?
Like, on the lips?

182
00:10:43,578 --> 00:10:45,646
Yeah. Have you?

183
00:10:46,247 --> 00:10:48,015
Not exactly.

184
00:10:48,048 --> 00:10:51,051
Neither have I,
but I practice a lot.

185
00:10:51,085 --> 00:10:52,419
You want to see?

186
